{"about_the_game":"Culinarium is a Card management cooking game where you can cook by stacking ingredients and employees on top of various kitchen tools.<br>You can think about it as Stacklands meeting Overcooked.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/newgif2bis.gif?t=1737454039\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/newgif4bis.gif?t=1737454039\" /><br><br>You open booster packs to get cards that you can then stack to make various dishes that you'll sell. With money you can buy more booster packs and unlock new ingredients, kitchen tools, and recipes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/newgif1bis.gif?t=1737454039\" /><br><br>You'll have to deal with random events from time to time like a rat trying to eat your ingredients, a fire, or a complicated food critic.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/new_gif_3_bis.gif?t=1737454039\" /><br><br>There are 2 game modes: <br>- An Adventure mode where you have to cook your way up across 4 Acts ( Italy, US, Japan and France ) to become the best chef. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/new_gif_5_bis.gif?t=1737454039\" /><br><br>- A free mode where you can cook the way you want.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/extras/newgif6bis.gif?t=1737454039\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737454039","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183870/page.bg.jpg?t=1737454039","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store